flowchart TB
    SII[Solvency II<br/>EU Risk-Based Capital Framework<br/>Effective 2016]

    SII --> P1[PILLAR 1<br/>Quantitative Requirements]
    SII --> P2[PILLAR 2<br/>Governance & Supervisory Review]
    SII --> P3[PILLAR 3<br/>Reporting & Disclosure]

    P1 --> TechProv[Technical Provisions<br/>Best estimate of liabilities<br/>plus risk margin]
    P1 --> SCR[Solvency Capital Requirement<br/>99.5% 1-year VaR<br/>Standard formula or internal model]
    P1 --> MCR[Minimum Capital Requirement<br/>Lower threshold<br/>triggers supervisory action]
    P1 --> OwnFunds[Own Funds<br/>Tier 1, 2, 3 capital<br/>Must cover SCR]

    P2 --> ORSA[ORSA<br/>Own Risk & Solvency Assessment<br/>Forward-looking risk review]
    P2 --> Governance[Governance<br/>Risk management, actuarial,<br/>internal audit, compliance]
    P2 --> FitProper[Fit & Proper<br/>Key function holders]

    P3 --> SFCR[SFCR<br/>Solvency & Financial<br/>Condition Report<br/>Public annual disclosure]
    P3 --> RSR[RSR<br/>Regular Supervisory Report<br/>Private to supervisor]
    P3 --> QRT[QRTs<br/>Quantitative Reporting<br/>Templates quarterly/annual]

    SCR --> StdFormula[Standard Formula<br/>Prescribed factors]
    SCR --> Internal[Internal Model<br/>Company-built,<br/>regulator-approved]

    Internal --> Approval[Multi-year approval process<br/>with national supervisor]

    EIOPA[EIOPA<br/>Coordinates supervision]
    NationalReg[National Regulators<br/>BaFin, ACPR, IVASS,<br/>Bank of Spain DGSFP]

    EIOPA -.coordinates.-> NationalReg
    NationalReg -.supervises.-> SII

